<span class="image-message">[Insert Image: Account Login Interface]</span>

<h3>4.3.2 Admin Dashboard and Inventory Processing</h3>
<p>When the admin logs in, they see the main dashboard with statistics showing live orders and total income. Under the Inventory page, the admin can click "Add Cake" to open a form. This form allows the admin to set the base cake details and quickly add multiple different sizes, shapes, and flavors with their specific prices.</p>
