<h3>4.3.3 Customer Home and Catalog</h3>
<p>The customer's home screen shows beautiful promotional banners and a "Best Sellers" section that automatically lists the cakes bought most often. The Catalog page lets users search for specific cakes by typing or filtering by categories like 'Birthday' or 'Anniversary'.</p>
