<h3>4.3.6 Order Tracking and History</h3>
<p>After an order is placed, the customer can view a tracking page. This page has a visual timeline with steps: New, Confirmed, Preparing, Ready, and Delivered. The steps light up with different colors as the admin updates the order status.</p>
<span class="image-message">[Insert Image: Timeline Order Tracker]</span>

<h3>4.3.7 Order Verification Queue (Admin)</h3>
<p>The admin order table lists all pending orders. Clicking an order opens a side panel. This panel shows what the customer ordered, any special requests, and displays the image of the bank payment slip that the customer uploaded so the admin can verify it.</p>
